Very windy- but clear and hot
Wind finally dieted down enough to take a decent reading.  The sun came out too.

Finally another calm and sunny day to take a reading.  Lake was churned up badly over the Labor Day weekend.  Many more boats than usual pulling tubes and skiers.  Just what the lake was intended for.

Nice day- a little choppy on the lake but not too bad
Finally a sunny day without a lot of wind or wave action.  Water has tiny white spots floating in the water... think it is some of the seaweed releasing seed pods.

Great for taking a reading- clear sky and very light breeze
